Package: dummyosp
Type: Package
Title: Dummy Package to Test R-Universe Dependency Installation
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R:
    person("Felix", "Mil", email = "felix.mil@esqlabs.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A minimal package that imports ospsuite and ospsuite.plots. Its only
    purpose is to verify that packages depending on the Open-Systems-Pharmacology
    R-universe packages can be installed with their dependencies resolved from the
    universe.
